        "icon": "document",
        "body": "<p>Maison Amiir ensures premium packaging, safe handling, and smooth delivery for every order.</p><p><strong>1. Dispatch Time</strong><br>Orders are processed and shipped within 1–3 working days of payment confirmation.</p><p><strong>2. Shipping Charges</strong><br>Shipping charges are displayed at checkout and may vary based on your delivery location (Currenlty we offer free delivery across india).</p><p><strong>3. Express Delivery Timeline</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Metro cities: 1 – 3 working days</li>\n<li>Non-metro cities &amp; towns: 3 – 6 working days</li>\n</ul><p><strong>4. No Cash on Delivery</strong><br>Maison Amiir does not offer Cash on Delivery. All orders must be prepaid.</p><p><strong>5. Domestic and International Shipping</strong><br>Domestic Delivery: We offer hassle-free, doorstep delivery across India to ensure your order arrives safely and conveniently.\n<br>International Shipping: We provide global delivery through our trusted international shipping partners to serve customers worldwide.<br>International Taxes and Duties: Please note that for international orders, applicable customs duties, local taxes, and shipping fees are calculated separately at checkout based on your destination country.\n\n.</p><p><strong>6. Order Tracking</strong><br>You can easily track your package under the Account section of our website. Additionally, a direct tracking link will be sent to you via WhatsApp or SMS as soon as your order ships..</p><p><strong>7. Courier Damage Protocol</strong><br>If your product arrives damaged, you must contact our customer support within 24 hours of delivery. Please provide:</p><ul>\n<li>An unboxing video (start to end, without interruption)</li>\n<li>Clear photos of the damaged product and packaging</li>\n<li>Proof of damage submitted within 24 hours of delivery, In few case you will ask to take live video call to proof the damage</li>\n</ul><p>Failure to provide the above within the stipulated time may result in your claim being declined.</p><p><strong>8. Replacement &amp; Refund for Transit Damage</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Replacement will be arranged at no extra charge upon verification of the damage.</li>\n<li>Refund will be issued only if the product cannot be replaced (out of stock), processed within 3–7 working days.</li>\n</ul>"
